('Costa Rica', 'Asylum Seekers', 'Documentation', 'none', 'Positive steps taken by the Government of Costa Rica with the support of UNHCR in providing temporary provisional documentation for asylum-seekers on an individual basis at no cost.\r\n\r\n', '', 'none', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'moderate', 'Unfortunately, in some cases, this temporary document for asylum seekers is not well known, especially in service providers and other various bodies and entities. ', '', '', '', '', ''),
