('Costa Rica', 'Refugees', 'Documentation', 'moderate', 'The 2010 Migration Act, its 2011 Refugee Regulation and the Social Security Regulations specify that, to renew their documents, refugees must be enrolled in the Social Security system , to which a mandatory fee is required, and their payments have to be up-to-date in order to renew their documentation. These  costs (68 USD per person added to costs related to the compulsory enrollment to the Social Security) are unaffordable for many refugees, particularly those with large families. In turn, this prevents them from accessing fundamental rights, including health. ', 'women,men,girls,boys,olderwomen,oldermen,femalesdisabilities,malesdisabilities,lgbtipersons', 'moderate', 'The 2010 Migration Act, its 2011 Refugee Regulation and the Social Security Regulations specify that, to renew their documents, refugees must be enrolled in the Social Security system , to which a mandatory fee is required, and their payments have to be up-to-date in order to renew their documentation. These  costs (68 USD per person added to costs related to the compulsory enrollment to the Social Security) are unaffordable for many refugees, particularly those with large families. In turn, this prevents them from accessing fundamental rights, including health. ', 'women,men,girls,boys,olderwomen,oldermen,femalesdisabilities,malesdisabilities,lgbtipersons', '', '', '', 'moderate', 'Hi legal and administrative fees to renew the refugee identification is a barrier for many refugees to access documentation and therefore effective rights.\r\n', 'women,men,girls,boys,olderwomen,oldermen,femalesdisabilities,malesdisabilities,lgbtipersons', 'unknown', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Operational', 'moderate', 'Some PoC couldn\'t access specific programmes such as poverty eradication, vocational training and job integration due to the IT systems that cannot read 12 number digit ID of Refugees ', ''),
