('Costa Rica', 'Refugees', 'Right to Work and Rights at Work', 'none', 'According to the national legislation refugees fully enjoy the same  rights and obligations in respect to labour law, as Costa Rican nationals.', 'women,men,girls,boys,olderwomen,oldermen,femalesdisabilities,malesdisabilities,lgbtipersons', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'moderate', 'Difficulties in demonstrating their level of education.\r\nEmployers are not aware o the steps for affiliating refugees to the Social Security. \r\nAs for individual businesses, ', '', 'moderate', '', '', 'moderate', 'Difficulties in demonstrating their level of education and provide with previous work references.\r\n\r\nDiscrimination based on migratory status, age, and nationality. ', 'girls,boys,olderwomen,oldermen,femalesdisabilities,malesdisabilities,lgbtipersons', 'moderate', 'Employers are not aware of labour rights of Refugies and the steps for affiliating them to the Social Security. ', '', 'recognition of level of education', 'moderate', '', ''),
