('Hungary', 'Returnees', 'Documentation', '', 'This position is a Business Analyst role critical for our day to day analytics, reporting and processes functioning.\r\nYou will be supporting/leading (task driven) the solution architecture enabling analytics and reporting within the team while also contributing to a centralized data pool which should allow for advanced insights into the performance of the Enterprise Infrastructure division from a cost, delivery and compute power perspective.\r\nExperience working with various data sets sourced from numerous platforms (flat files and automated data feeds) and merging these into a single coherent data set leveraging automated processes is important for this role.1', '', 'significant', 'This position is a Business Analyst role critical for our day to day analytics, reporting and processes functioning.\r\nYou will be supporting/leading (task driven) the solution architecture enabling analytics and reporting within the team while also contributing to a centralized data pool which should allow for advanced insights into the performance of the Enterprise Infrastructure division from a cost, delivery and compute power perspective.\r\nExperience working with various data sets sourced from numerous platforms (flat files and automated data feeds) and merging these into a single coherent data set leveraging automated processes is important for this role.2', '', 'moderate', 'This position is a Business Analyst role critical for our day to day analytics, reporting and processes functioning.\r\nYou will be supporting/leading (task driven) the solution architecture enabling analytics and reporting within the team while also contributing to a centralized data pool which should allow for advanced insights into the performance of the Enterprise Infrastructure division from a cost, delivery and compute power perspective.\r\nExperience working with various data sets sourced from numerous platforms (flat files and automated data feeds) and merging these into a single coherent data set leveraging automated processes is important for this role.3', '', 'none', 'This position is a Business Analyst role critical for our day to day analytics, reporting and processes functioning.\r\nYou will be supporting/leading (task driven) the solution architecture enabling analytics and reporting within the team while also contributing to a centralized data pool which should allow for advanced insights into the performance of the Enterprise Infrastructure division from a cost, delivery and compute power perspective.\r\nExperience working with various data sets sourced from numerous platforms (flat files and automated data feeds) and merging these into a single coherent data set leveraging automated processes is important for this role.4', '', 'unknown', 'This position is a Business Analyst role critical for our day to day analytics, reporting and processes functioning.\r\nYou will be supporting/leading (task driven) the solution architecture enabling analytics and reporting within the team while also contributing to a centralized data pool which should allow for advanced insights into the performance of the Enterprise Infrastructure division from a cost, delivery and compute power perspective.\r\nExperience working with various data sets sourced from numerous platforms (flat files and automated data feeds) and merging these into a single coherent data set leveraging automated processes is important for this role.5', '', '', 'This position is a Business Analyst role critical for our day to day analytics, reporting and processes functioning.\r\nYou will be supporting/leading (task driven) the solution architecture enabling analytics and reporting within the team while also contributing to a centralized data pool which should allow for advanced insights into the performance of the Enterprise Infrastructure division from a cost, delivery and compute power perspective.\r\nExperience working with various data sets sourced from numerous platforms (flat files and automated data feeds) and merging these into a single coherent data set leveraging automated processes is important for this role.6', '', 'significant', 'This position is a Business Analyst role critical for our day to day analytics, reporting and processes functioning.\r\nYou will be supporting/leading (task driven) the solution architecture enabling analytics and reporting within the team while also contributing to a centralized data pool which should allow for advanced insights into the performance of the Enterprise Infrastructure division from a cost, delivery and compute power perspective.\r\nExperience working with various data sets sourced from numerous platforms (flat files and automated data feeds) and merging these into a single coherent data set leveraging automated processes is important for this role.7', '', '', 'moderate', 'This position is a Business Analyst role critical for our day to day analytics, reporting and processes functioning.\r\nYou will be supporting/leading (task driven) the solution architecture enabling analytics and reporting within the team while also contributing to a centralized data pool which should allow for advanced insights into the performance of the Enterprise Infrastructure division from a cost, delivery and compute power perspective.\r\nExperience working with various data sets sourced from numerous platforms (flat files and automated data feeds) and merging these into a single coherent data set leveraging automated processes is important for this role.8', ''),
